11#include "p2p/client/turn_port_factory.h"
12
13#include <memory>
14#include <utility>
15
16#include "p2p/base/port_allocator.h"
17#include "p2p/base/turn_port.h"
18
19namespace cricket {
20
21TurnPortFactory::~TurnPortFactory() {}
22
23std::unique_ptr<Port> TurnPortFactory::Create(
24 const CreateRelayPortArgs& args,
25 rtc::AsyncPacketSocket* udp_socket) {
26 auto port = TurnPort::CreateUnique(
27 args.network_thread, args.socket_factory, args.network, udp_socket,
28 args.username, args.password, *args.server_address,
29 args.config->credentials, args.config->priority, args.origin,
30 args.turn_customizer);
31 if (!port)
32 return nullptr;
33 port->SetTlsCertPolicy(args.config->tls_cert_policy);
34 port->SetTurnLoggingId(args.config->turn_logging_id);
35 return std::move(port);
36}
37
38std::unique_ptr<Port> TurnPortFactory::Create(const CreateRelayPortArgs& args,
39 int min_port,
40 int max_port) {
41 auto port = TurnPort::CreateUnique(
42 args.network_thread, args.socket_factory, args.network, min_port,
43 max_port, args.username, args.password, *args.server_address,
44 args.config->credentials, args.config->priority, args.origin,
45 args.config->tls_alpn_protocols, args.config->tls_elliptic_curves,
46 args.turn_customizer, args.config->tls_cert_verifier);
47 if (!port)
48 return nullptr;
49 port->SetTlsCertPolicy(args.config->tls_cert_policy);
50 port->SetTurnLoggingId(args.config->turn_logging_id);
51 return std::move(port);
52}
53
54} // namespace cricket
